# Source: https://docs.vllm.ai/en/v0.24.0/api/vllm/model_executor/kernels/linear/
# Module: vllm.model_executor.kernels.linear, init_nvfp4_linear_kernel
VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT forces NVFP4 linear to use the CUTLASS backend for deterministic execution.
VLLM_BATCH_INVARIANT overrides --linear-backend=%s; using the CUTLASS backend for deterministic execution.
